                                State</gloss></hi></head>
                    <opener><dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi></placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-05-19T21:00:00+01:00">May 19, 1919—9
